# Pipeline INPUT zone. Drop raw HTML (for `convert`) or .md (for index/export/
# lint/scan) here; subfolders are allowed (e.g. inbox/sample/). With the
# workspace contract on (default), every pipeline input must live under this
# folder. Source files dropped here are git-ignored — only this skeleton is
# tracked. Set PIPELINE_ENFORCE_WORKSPACE=false to bypass the contract.
